      <a href="index.html" class="footer__logo">
        <img src="img/logo-wh-h.png" alt="Arctium Design" class="footer__logo-img" />
      </a>
      <p>© 2026 Arctium Design · Jenni Klette · Ludwigsfelde</p>
      <p class="footer__small">Grafik &amp; Print · Logogestaltung · Druckabwicklung</p>
